item.description: Quotes Customers don’t measure you on how hard you tried, they measure you on what you delivered ~Steve Jobs You’ve got to start with the customer experience and work back toward the technology - not the other way around ~ Steve Jobs Every man has two lives, and the second one starts when he realizes that he only has one. ~ Confucius
